"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?37/52/38727/abstract/1\">",
"      Mayer EA, Berman S, Derbyshire SW, et al. The effect of the 5-HT3 receptor antagonist, alosetron, on brain responses to visceral stimulation in irritable bowel syndrome patients. Aliment Pharmacol Ther 2002; 16:1357.",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li>",
"     <a class=\"nounderline abstract\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?37/52/38727/abstract/2\">",
